<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>ARCH&#160;552.  Architectural Design II.  6 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Introduction to the architectural design discipline as an organizer of quantities and as a function of argument and scenario. Exercises confront issues of size, number, expediency, and activity through diagramming, modeling, and graphic techniques. Course Information: Previously listed as ARCH 452. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=ARCH%20551" title="ARCH&#160;551" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ARCH 551');">ARCH&#160;551</a>.<br />
